      <p>Welcome home. We’re here to help you get a fresh start. Here you’ll find job training, housing support, legal aid, and more.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Job Training:</strong> Programs to build your skills and get you working.</li>
        <li><strong>Housing Assistance:</strong> Find safe, affordable places to live.</li>
        <li><strong>ID & Documents:</strong> Help getting your ID, social security card, and more.</li>
        <li><strong>Mental Health Services:</strong> Talk to someone who understands what you're going through.</li>
        <li><strong>Mentorship:</strong> Connect with someone who has walked this path.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="helpers" class="section alt">
      <h2>Get Involved</h2>
      <p>You can make a real difference. Support the reentry process and help reduce recidivism through direct action or donations.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Volunteer:</strong> Mentor, teach, or just be a supportive listener.</li>
        <li><strong>Hire:</strong> Offer job opportunities to skilled, motivated individuals.</li>
        <li><strong>Donate:</strong> Fund programs that provide housing, education, and legal support.</li>
        <li><strong>Advocate:</strong> Support policy changes and reentry reform.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
